{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"subheading":"","show_title":true,"heading_font_size":"heading-large","show_content":true,"text_font_size":"body-medium","align_text":"text-left","width":"wrapper","color_scheme":"","padding_top":50,"padding_bottom":50,"heading_tag":"automatic"}},"section_hero_AxQ3Ue":{"type":"section-hero","blocks":{"heading_kgHa7z":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"The Lustrous Story of Solarii Jewelry","heading_font_size":"heading-medium","heading_tag":"automatic"}}},"block_order":["heading_kgHa7z"],"settings":{"image_1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/26362356-1033-42d6-b82d-6c6661d3bfae.jpg","link":"","width":"wrapper--full","height":"screen-height-three-quarters","flex_align_desktop":"align--middle-center-desktop","content_width":50,"mobile_height":"screen-height-two-thirds--mobile","flex_align_mobile":"align--middle-center-mobile","color_scheme":"scheme-2","show_text_background":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"show_placeholder":true}},"section_text_with_products_AjA3QR":{"type":"section-text-with-products","settings":{"subheading":"","heading":"At Solarii, we began as gemstone enthusiasts with a passion for discovering beauty. We soon realized jewelry is more than looks—it holds emotions and dreams. Seeing the challenges people faced with cost, loss, and value, we created Solarii to bring light and positivity through every crafted piece.","width":"wrapper","text_font_size_px_desktop":22,"text_align_desktop":"text-left","text_font_size_px_mobile":18,"text_align_mobile":"text-left--mobile","color_scheme":"scheme-9c9f1fe6-23f9-471e-b2f3-03a31f5fb70d","padding_top":13,"padding_bottom":17}},"double-1":{"type":"section-double","blocks":{"text-1-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>At Solarii, our story began with a group of young gemstone enthusiasts, driven by an unwavering passion to discover the world’s most beautiful stones. Along our journey, we realized that jewelry isn’t just about aesthetics—it’s about the emotions and dreams they carry. We saw people struggle with the loss of a precious ring, the steep cost of the perfect piece, or the frustration of diamonds that didn’t hold their value. So, we created Solarii, with a vision to bring light and positivity through every meticulously crafted piece of jewelry.<br\/><\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","padding_bottom":16}}},"block_order":["text-1-1"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"image_1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/fetchpik.com-KLZ9NGITwj.jpg","image_width":"one-half","text_alignment":"text-left","layout":"is-reversed","width":"wrapper--full","height":"image-height","mobile_height":"image-height--mobile","reverse_blocks":false,"color_scheme":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":50,"show_placeholder":true}},"columns":{"type":"section-columns","blocks":{"image-1":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/482752379_18400709851096754_3018536975705798109_n.jpg","image_width":100,"image_shape":"normal","title":"","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>At Solarii Jewelry, we see jewelry as more than adornment—it reflects your inner self. Our designs embody feminine elegance and strength, each piece a radiant symbol that lets you shine.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","button_text":"SHOP NOW","button_url":"shopify:\/\/collections\/buy-1-get-1-free","button_type":"btn--primary","button_size":"","button_style":"btn--text","show_arrow":false,"image_aspect_ratio":1.3,"mobile_image_aspect_ratio":1.3,"heading_tag":"automatic"}},"image-2":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/478846094_18398076388096754_6250403410627802111_n.jpg","image_width":100,"image_shape":"normal","title":"","heading_font_size":"heading-small","text":"<p>At Solarii Jewelry, every piece is handcrafted with care for the environment. From materials to production, we minimize our footprint and pursue ever more sustainable practices.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","button_text":"SHOP NOW","butt